WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.380 --> 00:00:01.160
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.160 --> 00:00:02.876
How are you all doing today?

00:00:03.213 --> 00:00:04.227
Praise the Lord.

00:00:04.227 --> 00:00:15.939
I had a dream last night, and the Lord spoke to me, warning me to warn you all about watching your children during the holiday season.

00:00:15.939 --> 00:00:19.654
When you're going out shopping, don't get distracted.

00:00:21.475 --> 00:00:30.880
If you take them into a mall or a major retail store, don't get distracted with your surroundings.

00:00:30.880 --> 00:01:06.297
I saw that there was a plan while people were distracted; they had children wandering around, going off from them a little bit to look at presents or something from the store.

00:01:06.297 --> 00:01:15.680
These were younger kids, probably ten years old and younger.

00:01:23.987 --> 00:01:35.940
I saw men watching the children and watching the parents secretly, as if they didn't know they were being followed.

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:47.640
These mothers were distracted with all the other kids.

00:01:47.640 --> 00:02:00.862
If you had two or three kids with you, you would be distracted with shopping because the places were full of people.

00:02:00.862 --> 00:02:23.583
As the other kid would wander off, I saw the men assigned to grab these children for bad intentions.

00:02:38.480 --> 00:02:38.750
This is something we can pray against today.

00:02:38.750 --> 00:02:50.850
I've seen in the comments where people ask, "Where did the 350,000 kids go?

00:02:50.850 --> 00:03:00.689
" After my son brought that up, I had this dream.

00:03:00.689 --> 00:03:24.280
I know when the Lord's speaking to me because I wake up and can't stop thinking about it all day; it's stirring in my spirit.

00:03:26.695 --> 00:03:42.750
I believe the Lord is warning me to warn you all so that you are on guard.

00:03:45.570 --> 00:04:06.408
I've warned you about being in public places already because of people doing stupid things with mass shootings and big events.

00:04:07.639 --> 00:04:35.540
I am praying over the Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade next week, Rockin' New Year's Eve, Atlanta—because He showed me Atlanta—the shopping malls, and events in general because it's a very active time of year.

00:04:39.280 --> 00:04:45.300
This was just another thing the Lord brought up to tell people: watch your children.

00:04:45.300 --> 00:05:07.425
Do not walk in fear; it's not a call to fear, but a call to prayer so that your antenna is up.

00:05:07.425 --> 00:05:23.479
Keep your antennas up because the enemy has a plan all the time to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:05:23.479 --> 00:05:42.109
We pray against those plans so that people are watching their kids and their surroundings when they go shopping.

00:05:42.109 --> 00:05:55.892
It's an exciting time, and people are not paying attention because they are looking at sales.

00:05:57.224 --> 00:06:12.720
I wanted to shed some light on an enemy plan to kidnap children and take them into slavery.

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:28.551
I've been praying over the war, interceding for what I believe would be an acceleration of what I've seen coming.

00:06:28.898 --> 00:06:54.902
I believe the Lord wants to give us a window of extended grace and favor, turning things around with the economy.

00:07:09.866 --> 00:07:10.693
I've told you all about the attack against the economy and the house of cards falling.

00:07:10.693 --> 00:07:42.714
My son is making a video for you right now, and this was the Antichrist flag that the Lord showed me when I went to tribulation with Jesus.

00:07:50.406 --> 00:08:02.919
This is what the Antichrist will raise up and put on all the buildings whenever he is ruling.

00:08:04.845 --> 00:08:17.760
He makes you take down your country's flag and put up his.

00:08:17.760 --> 00:08:39.120
I tried to the best of my ability to remember the five stars representing the five pillars of Islam.

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:55.653
It is very interesting, like the UN logo, but this is the old Afghan flag from the 2000s.

00:08:55.653 --> 00:09:08.080
After Afghanistan fell, it was the Northern Alliance flag that this actually looks like.

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:21.104
My son made this, and it came right out of my spirit.

00:09:21.104 --> 00:09:41.692
When somebody said it looked like the Northern Afghanistan Alliance flag, I was like, "What?

00:09:42.959 --> 00:10:01.349
" I bring all this up to rehash it because there are a lot of new faces here.

00:10:01.349 --> 00:10:09.354
I'm grateful for every single one of you subscribing.

00:10:23.154 --> 00:10:32.545
I was out in the garage praying, and I heard the Lord tell me, "Trump will be known as a wartime president.

00:10:50.995 --> 00:10:51.373
" I thought, "Well, that's not good.

00:10:51.373 --> 00:11:00.909
" I asked the Lord for the direction of 2025.

00:11:00.909 --> 00:11:16.006
Are we going to have a major crash or see the house of cards fall?

00:11:16.006 --> 00:11:35.571
I was praying over the plague I've seen coming, the economy, and the new digital platform they're birthing.

00:11:45.366 --> 00:12:02.543
The Lord showed me key people in NATO were trying to stir up this war because Trump was going to try to pull out completely and not fund the Ukrainian thing.

00:12:06.375 --> 00:12:22.720
The Lord showed me Trump would try to strong-arm Putin, but the Lord said, "You will not be able to strong-arm Putin this way.

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:34.251
" He'll have to handle him with caution because things have escalated rapidly.

00:12:40.276 --> 00:12:58.615
We have to pray he has supernatural wisdom on how to walk around landmines because you're dealing with an aggressive enemy that is like a wounded animal.

00:13:08.839 --> 00:13:09.204
This war has been going on for four years.

00:13:09.204 --> 00:13:45.480
Emmanuel Macron has been kind of quiet since President Trump was announced, but I told you the UK would be involved, supplying missiles and trying to provoke a major World War III by sending these long-range weapons.

00:13:45.480 --> 00:13:54.213
Biden is going alongside it, saying they're innocent while giving these weapons.

00:13:54.213 --> 00:14:14.173
They're saying if you do this, we're going to use weapons we've never used before—weapons of mass destruction, major artillery.

00:14:14.173 --> 00:14:23.434
Old Cold War alliances are trying to stir up again.

00:14:26.484 --> 00:14:36.851
The Lord showed me they would try to bring down the dollar through BRICS and other things.

00:14:36.851 --> 00:14:56.669
They were watching to see how President Trump or Kamala Harris would handle the next phases because they had a plan both ways.

00:15:00.631 --> 00:15:02.244
I believe it's through an acceleration of war.

00:15:10.799 --> 00:15:11.079
The Lord told me there are very sobering days ahead.

00:15:11.079 --> 00:15:25.544
How the body of Christ will get through this is by being filled with the Holy Spirit.

00:15:25.544 --> 00:16:02.475
In these last days, you will have to maintain a spirit of joy and keep yourself under the umbrella of His protection, understanding your covenant and walking in your authority in Psalm 91 and Psalm 23.

00:16:02.475 --> 00:16:22.069
I believe with all my heart we will see the plague; it will come and do what the Bible said: plagues and pestilences.

00:16:22.069 --> 00:16:25.650
Do we fear it?

00:16:25.650 --> 00:16:33.949
No, but we are here for the birthing pains.

00:16:33.949 --> 00:16:43.260
As labor pains upon a woman, they get more intense.

00:16:43.260 --> 00:16:52.100
He said He would always provide for and take care of His beloved.

00:16:52.100 --> 00:17:00.690
We walk with wisdom and pray over what He tells us.

00:17:00.690 --> 00:17:20.413
The body of Christ must rise up more than ever and take authority so that the devil does not get a foothold.

00:17:20.413 --> 00:17:45.494
The Lord told me, "When the election's over is not when this starts; it's when you put your foot on the gas even harder, interceding for what's coming.

00:17:45.494 --> 00:18:02.782
" The enemy has a plan, and we are to put a kink in his hose.

00:18:03.853 --> 00:18:12.474
I have a book right here called "The Ultimate Voice" by Oral Roberts.

00:18:12.474 --> 00:18:17.110
Diana is reading with me now.

00:18:17.110 --> 00:18:26.693
She's been helping me answer emails; it's been crazy, hasn't it, babe?

00:18:26.693 --> 00:18:49.112
This was the last book Oral Roberts ever wrote in his 90s, and there are nuggets in here on how to hear the voice of the Lord for yourself.

00:19:05.484 --> 00:19:05.756
You don't need a prophet to hear about investments or where you're supposed to live.

00:19:14.600 --> 00:19:14.984
You have the Holy Spirit inside you.

00:19:14.984 --> 00:19:23.502
Reading books like this fans the flame.

00:19:23.502 --> 00:19:26.399
Diana, read that passage.

00:19:26.399 --> 00:19:39.636
[Diana reads]: "God will call you to become an extension to others of what He has done in your life.

00:19:43.720 --> 00:19:59.628
The area of your life that God heals is very likely the area of service He wants you to extend to others.

00:20:05.885 --> 00:20:20.199
The person who has been healed emotionally from abuse becomes a healer to those who are abused.

00:20:33.275 --> 00:20:35.799
The person who has been healed physically becomes a nurse or physician.

00:20:35.799 --> 00:20:51.832
No person can minister God’s love to another person beyond his level of personal experience.

00:20:53.248 --> 00:21:04.635
To minister God’s love, the other person must know that you have been where he is.

00:21:05.505 --> 00:21:29.540
You will find it difficult to believe for others to have a miracle unless you have experienced that miracle in your own life.

00:21:29.540 --> 00:21:47.280
Once you have experienced miracles, it is easy to believe for miracles in the lives of others.

00:21:47.280 --> 00:22:10.650
I have been a far more compassionate evangelist because I know what it means to have been sick.

00:22:10.650 --> 00:22:21.480
What He has done in you, He likely desires to do through you.

00:22:21.480 --> 00:22:26.200
" Do you see that?

00:22:26.200 --> 00:22:34.337
What have you come through in your life?

00:22:34.337 --> 00:22:59.371
God will use that pain to help someone else who is walking through it right now because you have compassion for it.

00:23:09.480 --> 00:23:09.800
We have more compassion for people with special needs.

00:23:09.800 --> 00:23:25.353
Every single time I see them, it makes me want to weep.

00:23:25.353 --> 00:23:38.430
When someone has walked through cancer, they have more compassion.

00:23:38.430 --> 00:24:11.737
When we went to Billy Burke, he said you will have an anointing for women that have children with special needs in the womb—with Down syndrome and things like that—because we've walked through that valley of the shadow of death.

00:24:11.737 --> 00:24:23.680
Diana and I stand with you for your kids and special needs children.

00:24:23.680 --> 00:24:41.564
We're going to pray over your children, this war, and protection as you go to the malls.

00:24:51.234 --> 00:24:55.724
Be like a military scout watching the wall; my kids aren't leaving my side.

00:25:02.159 --> 00:25:04.286
Father, I thank You for every person represented here today.

00:25:20.960 --> 00:25:25.413
We plead the blood of Jesus over their children and over the 350,000 who have disappeared coming over the border.

00:25:25.413 --> 00:25:44.154
I thank You, Father, that all hidden things be revealed, from sex trafficking to slavery and all kinds of evil.

00:25:51.902 --> 00:25:57.900
I call judgment down on the people who have done anything to these kids.

00:26:07.143 --> 00:26:51.222
You said it would be better to have never been born or have a millstone thrown around your neck and be dragged to the bottom of the ocean if you lay hands on one of these little children.

00:26:51.222 --> 00:27:19.960
Show the authorities, the Trump administration—when they come into power, they will find every single one of them and bring them to safety.

00:27:19.960 --> 00:27:26.706
Let all hidden things be revealed.

00:27:34.129 --> 00:28:06.310
We thank You, Lord, that the FBI and Homeland Security would find every single one of them, and the people who did anything harsh will be prosecuted.

00:28:06.310 --> 00:28:18.331
