00:29:51.853 --> 00:29:59.820
Now, Father, we lift up the war.

00:30:11.960 --> 00:30:17.580
We thank You that there is a kink in the enemy's plan and an exposing of this in Jesus' name.

00:30:22.510 --> 00:30:32.137
